nexus-mail-amd64 (1.0.0-1) focal; urgency=medium

  * Initial release for AMD64 architecture
  * NexusMP: IMAP4rev1 server with IDLE, compression, TLS support
  * NexusMTA: Mail Transfer Agent with queue management
  * NexusSMTP: SMTP server for mail submission
  * NexusRMC: Remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF

